						               													<description>Accomplish your Guild's hidden agenda through low blows and tricky interruptions during the opponent's turn that will increase the complexity and tension of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Ploy is a new type of card which comes along with its own several abilities. &amp;#10;A Ploy Card, with its asymmetric and secret new strategy, may allow you to beat your opponent, overwriting the rules of the game in specific conditions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The new Ploy cards provide alternative ways to interact with the opponent, even during their turn, to sabotage their strategies when needed. A Ploy card must remain face down until they are played, but Ploys can also be drawn, forcefully revealed, swapped, or removed by the effect of other abilities during the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Volfyirion Guilds Ploy Expansion is not a standalone game. &amp;#10;It can be played either with Volfyirion, or Volfyirion Guilds in 1vs1 mode. &amp;#10;The Ploy Expansion can be combined with Volfyirion, Volfyirion Guilds, or any other expansion, for an even more challenging experience. In any case we do not recommend combining more than two expansions at the same time.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
